title: Thadaiyara Thaakka
subTitle: Selva plans to expand his business and settle down, but circumstances pit him against Maha, a loan shark. However, when Maha suddenly dies, Kumar, his brother, blames Selva and seeks revenge.

title: Sooriya Nagaram
subTitle: Two lovers belonging to different communities face opposition from the girl's father, who is the head of his community. Initially, her brother supports her, but he soon gives in to societal pressure.

title: Thai Naadu
subTitle: A righteous man wages war against the corrupt government officials to save the people. But he and his family start getting death threats when he exposes a few corrupt politicians.

title: Teleshopping
subTitle: Learn about a wide selection of products and take advantage of a convenient method of shopping. A show for those who love to shop from the comforts of their home.

title: Kunguma Pottu Gounder
subTitle: Kandasamy is desperate to enrol his son in a good school. Trouble ensues when his wife spots him with an educated woman who is posing as their child's mother in order to help him get admission.

title: Annai
subTitle: Maha, a rich widow, lets Anjali, a young orphan, live in her house for a month every year. Problems arise when Anjali criticises Maha's behaviour.

title: Pagal Nilavu
subTitle: Selvam is indebted to Devarajan, a big shot in town, for saving his mother. When he falls in love with the sister of the new police inspector, Devarajan plans to make good use of the situation.

title: Rojavanam
subTitle: Muthu, an employee at an orphanage, falls in love with the daughter of the owner, Roja. However, things become complicated when it is revealed that she is to be married to someone else.

title: Padikkadavan
subTitle: Two brothers are ousted from their house by their stepbrother's wife. Years later, when one of the brothers is framed for a murder, his stepbrother, who is a judge, returns as a lawyer to save him.

title: Adhe Neram Adhe Idam
subTitle: After Janani accepts his proposal, Karthik leaves for Australia to continue his studies. However, fate takes a decisive turn when he learns that she has agreed to marry another man in his absence.

title: Adhe Neram Adhe Idam

title: Yaarukku Theriyum
subTitle: A group of six people regain consciousness and find themselves locked in a warehouse. While trying to remember their past, the individuals grapple with a host of emotions.

title: A Film By Aravind
subTitle: Director Aravind and actor Rishi go on a road trip to find inspiration for their next film. However, they turn into real-life characters as a script dictates the events in their lives.

title: Fillers
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of promotional videos and trailers of Bollywood movies featuring popular actors and actresses.

title: Nandinee
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Vasantha Ragam
subTitle: A man confesses his love to a woman and gets married to her. However, chaos ensues when his wife's beloved from the past, who was known to be dead, appears all of a sudden.

title: Uyarntha Ullam
subTitle: Anand, a drunkard, gets into a brawl and is saved by Selvam, whom he appoints as his personal assistant. Later, he falls in love with Geetha and decides to transform his lifestyle.

title: Ranga
subTitle: Ranganathan takes the path of a criminal while looking for work. However, trouble arises when he goes on a mission to kidnap a child and encounters a friend from the past.

title: Vennila Kabadi Kuzhu 2
subTitle: When a young man uncovers the truth about his father's passion for kabaddi, he sets out to become a kabaddi player and fulfill his father's unrealised ambition in the sport.

title: Snegithiye
subTitle: When Radhika lies about being with a man called Ramesh to avoid marriage, someone with that name contacts her and claims to be her boyfriend. However, he is murdered and Radhika becomes a suspect.

title: Amma
subTitle: Two siblings fall for two sisters; however, one's love is unrequited. Enraged, he assaults the woman and gets himself killed when she defends herself. Her sibling, driven by loyalty, claims responsibility for the fatal act.

title: Pooveli
subTitle: When a man helps his classmate after the death of her lover, her family mistakes him for her husband. But the girl tries to make her family hate him so that he can go on with his life.

title: Kabadi Kabadi
subTitle: Pandian falls in love with his neighbour, Maithili, and anonymously helps her continue her education. However, Pandian's roommate, Prakash, gets all the credits for his good deeds.

title: Athiradi Vettai
subTitle: When a truck collides with his car, an exemplary politician goes into a coma. His police officer son learns that the accident is a deliberate attack and sets out to hunt down the perpetrators and exact his revenge.

title: Veera Thalattu
subTitle: Pandi, a villager, loves his mother beyond words. However, Pandi gets shocked when his uncle reveals that she is not the one who gave birth to him.

title: Cheran Pandian
subTitle: Periya Gounder, bound by caste pride, mistreats his stepbrother Chinna. Howver, when his daughter falls for Chinna's relative, his beliefs are challenged.

title: Kilinjalgal
subTitle: When their parents disapprove of their relationship, Babu and Julie, two lovers belonging to different religious backgrounds, face several hardships.
